		<div id="comment_body_64466391"><p>That *is* interesting. How tall are the highest plants? How high is the atmosphere?<br>Is it possible for something to have more than one effect?<br>I'm pretty sure grain is duck food, what happens if we force-feed a duck two or three times its normal food portion?<br>Is the extra dose food or poison?</p></div>
	</div>

